    <div class="content-sidebar-wrap has-boxed-children">
     <main class="content" id="genesis-content">
      <article class="post-29814 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail category-city-guide tag-city-guide tag-kansas tag-safe tag-safety tag-suburb tag-suburban tag-suburban-living entry boxed" aria-label="Top 10 Safest Cities in Kansas">
       <header class="entry-header">
        <h1 class="entry-title">Top 10 Safest Cities in Kansas</h1>
       </header>
       <div class="entry-content">
        <figure class="wp-block-image size-large">
         <img loading="lazy" width="1000" height="563" src="https://www.newhomesource.com/learn/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kansas.jpg" alt="Kansas" class="wp-image-29774" srcset="https://www.newhomesource.com/learn/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kansas.jpg 1000w, https://www.newhomesource.com/learn/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kansas-600x338.jpg 600w, https://www.newhomesource.com/learn/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kansas-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.newhomesource.com/learn/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kansas-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px">
        </figure>
        <p>Welcome to <a href="https://www.newhomesource.com/state/kansas">Kansas</a>! The Sunflower State is one of the nation’s leading agricultural states, with its main crop being wheat and wheat products. But it’s not all farmland in Kansas – the state is also known for being an industrial leader in airplane manufacturing! Whether you’re drawn into the rural life or the urban craze, there’s a little something for everyone in Kansas. Ready to move and truly understand “there’s no place like home”? We’ve compiled a list of the safest cities in Kansas to help you make an informed decision.</p>
        <div class="lwptoc lwptoc-autoWidth lwptoc-white lwptoc-notInherit" data-smooth-scroll="1" data-smooth-scroll-offset="24">
         <div class="lwptoc_i">
          <div class="lwptoc_header"> <b class="lwptoc_title">Skip Ahead</b>
          </div>
          <div class="lwptoc_items lwptoc_items-visible">
           <div class="lwptoc_itemWrap">
            <div class="lwptoc_item"> <a href="#1-valley-center"> <span class="lwptoc_item_label">1. Valley Center</span> </a>
            </div>
            <div class="lwptoc_item"> <a href="#2-tonganoxie"> <span class="lwptoc_item_label">2. Tonganoxie</span> </a>
            </div>
            <div class="lwptoc_item"> <a href="#3-basehor"> <span class="lwptoc_item_label">3. Basehor</span> </a>
            </div>
            <div class="lwptoc_item"> <a href="#4-leawood"> <span class="lwptoc_item_label">4. Leawood</span> </a>
            </div>
            <div class="lwptoc_item"> <a href="#5-mcpherson"> <span class="lwptoc_item_label">5. McPherson</span> </a>
            </div>
            <div class="lwptoc_item"> <a href="#6-ulysses"> <span class="lwptoc_item_label">6. Ulysses</span> </a>
            </div>
            <div class="lwptoc_item"> <a href="#7-bel-aire"> <span class="lwptoc_item_label">7. Bel Aire</span> </a>
