          <div itemprop="description">
           <p>Sarah graduated from Trinity University in 2012 with a degree in International Relations and Political Science. She writes blogs on new homes, decor, communities, and more for&nbsp;<a class="c-link" href="http://newhomesource.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">NewHomeSource</a>. When she’s not writing, you can find her spending time with her three cats.</p>
